          "type": "rtf",
          "settings": {
            "richtext_content": "<p>Liam Harrison is a world-renowned Muay Thai champion and kickboxing icon, known for his powerful left hook and devastating low kick. With a career spanning decades and numerous world titles to his name, Liam has been number 1 in the UK rankings since the age of 17 and widely regarded as the best Muay Thai fighter to ever come out of the UK. As a Gym King ambassador, Liam brings the same grit, discipline, and relentless spirit that have made him a legend in the ring.</p>"
          }
        },
        "quote_DBX4Ty": {
          "type": "quote",
          "settings": {
            "quote_text": "Liam Harrison’s fights are a masterclass in aggression, technique, and heart. Watch him break down his approach to Muay Thai, offering a glimpse into what makes him one of the most feared fighters in the sport.",
            "quote_author": ""
          }
        },
